title: The Wedge Table
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. An extension of the The Wedge Coop. Offers a variety of freshly prepared food, soft-serve, and drinks, in addition to packaged to-go meals and a limited grocery section. A community room is available for rent along with a community kitchen. Patio available in warmer weather. Off-street parking on north side of building.
